race.comment: OUT OF AUSTRIA (6) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 19.84 beating Inland Mark. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. IRONGATE EXPRESS (3) recorded a win over the 300m at Q Straight in a decent 16.62 last start. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. GOLDSTAR VOGUE (2) turned in a fair 5th placed finish last time at this track over 352m (20.09). Worth another chance. TUTA TIMELINE (1) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.
